<subSubSection id="C368652E93588E05F2AAF9FBFCE6F96C" pageId="1" pageNumber="485" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BCD36A593588E05F2AAF9FBFCE6F96C" blockId="1.[151,1436,1641,2028]" pageId="1" pageNumber="485">
<materialsCitation id="3B1A3CF893588E05F2AAF9FBFCE2F96C" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3798147322" collectorName="J. Serrano" pageId="1" pageNumber="485" specimenCount="2" typeStatus="lectotype">
The specimen designated as 
<typeStatus id="54C9880793588E05F3EBF9FBFDECF948" box="[470,573,1641,1667]" pageId="1" pageNumber="485">lectotype</typeStatus>
is a male bearing the labels “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D2693588E05F1B9F9FBFBC2F948" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[900,1043,1641,1667]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Acupalpus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="485" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="metallescens">
<emphasis id="B906EAB793588E05F1B9F9FBFBC2F948" box="[900,1043,1641,1667]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="485">metallescens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
m. in Dalmatia” and “ 
<typeStatus id="54C9880793588E05F736F9FBFAAFF948" box="[1291,1406,1641,1667]" pageId="1" pageNumber="485">Lectotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D2693588E05F2AAF91FFD91F96C" authority="Dejean, 1829" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[151,576,1677,1703]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Acupalpus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="485" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="metallescens">
<emphasis id="B906EAB793588E05F2AAF91FFE72F96C" box="[151,419,1677,1703]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="485">Acupalpus metallescens</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493588E05F397F91FFD91F96C" author="Dejean, P. F. M. A." box="[426,576,1677,1703]" pageId="1" pageNumber="485" refId="ref10732" refString="Dejean, P. F. M. A. (1829) Species general des coleopteres de la collection de M. le Comte Dejean. Tome quatrieme. Mequignon- Marvis, Paris, vii + 520 pp." type="book" year="1829">Dejean, 1829</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
desig. by 
<collectorName id="2687537393588E05F08EF91CFCF8F96C" box="[691,809,1677,1704]" pageId="1" pageNumber="485">J. Serrano</collectorName>
”
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C368652E93588E06F2FAF923FF31FF1E" lastPageId="2" lastPageNumber="486" pageId="1" pageNumber="485" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BCD36A593588E05F2FAF923FA44F93B" blockId="1.[151,1436,1641,2028]" pageId="1" pageNumber="485">
The beetle from Dalmatia is hereby designated as 
<typeStatus id="54C9880793588E05F0D2F923FC82F900" box="[751,851,1713,1739]" pageId="1" pageNumber="485">lectotype</typeStatus>
taking into account that it is well preserved, matches the original description and labels, and also agrees with the current morphological concept of the species (see below).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCD36A593588E05F2FAF96BFC85F827" blockId="1.[151,1436,1641,2028]" pageId="1" pageNumber="485">
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493588E05F2FAF96BFE77F8D8" author="Jeannel, R." box="[199,422,1785,1811]" pageId="1" pageNumber="485" pagination="572 - 1173" refId="ref11231" refString="Jeannel, R. (1942) Coleopteres carabiques. Deuxieme partie. Faune de France 40. Librairie de la Faculte des Sciences, Paris, pp. 572 - 1173." type="book chapter" year="1942">Jeannel (1942: 728)</bibRefCitation>
wrote that the “type” came from 
<emphasis id="B906EAB793588E05F123F96BFC36F8D8" box="[798,999,1785,1811]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="485">
midi de la 
<collectingCountry id="F365763593588E05F1ABF968FC36F8D8" box="[918,999,1786,1811]" name="France" pageId="1" pageNumber="485">France</collectingCountry>
</emphasis>
, a comment without formal taxonomic value. 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493588E05F2DFF88CFEABF8FC" author="Wrase, D. W." box="[226,378,1821,1848]" pageId="1" pageNumber="485" pagination="889 - 899" refId="ref12584" refString="Wrase, D. W. (2009) On the identity of Amblystomus levantinus Reitter, 1893, and remarks on A. metallescens (Dejean, 1829) (Coleoptera, Carabidae, Harpalini, Amblystomina). Linzer Biologische Beitrage, 41, 889 - 899." type="journal article" year="2009">Wrase (2009)</bibRefCitation>
formally designed as 
<typeStatus id="54C9880793588E05F049F88CFD07F8F3" box="[628,726,1822,1848]" pageId="1" pageNumber="485">syntypes</typeStatus>
beetles deposited in the Collection Johann Friedrich Schüppel, MNHU, Berlin. Schüppel was an entomologist who was well-known for sending valuable material to Dejean, that became the basis for Dejean’s formal descriptions of many new species. 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493588E05F1E2F8F4FBA8F8B4" author="Wrase, D. W." box="[991,1145,1893,1920]" pageId="1" pageNumber="485" pagination="889 - 899" refId="ref12584" refString="Wrase, D. W. (2009) On the identity of Amblystomus levantinus Reitter, 1893, and remarks on A. metallescens (Dejean, 1829) (Coleoptera, Carabidae, Harpalini, Amblystomina). Linzer Biologische Beitrage, 41, 889 - 899." type="journal article" year="2009">Wrase (2009)</bibRefCitation>
published morphological details of 
<typeStatus id="54C9880793588E05F335F818FEBCF86F" box="[264,365,1930,1956]" pageId="1" pageNumber="485">syntypes</typeStatus>
, including the illustration of male aedeagus. Although I have not dissected the aedeagus of the 
<typeStatus id="54C9880793588E05F2AAF83FFED0F80C" box="[151,257,1965,1991]" pageId="1" pageNumber="485">lectotype</typeStatus>
, its external morphology agrees with that described in the works of 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493588E05F1C9F83CFB42F80C" author="Fuente de la, J. M." box="[1012,1171,1965,1992]" pageId="1" pageNumber="485" refId="ref10490" refString="Fuente de la, J. M. (1927) Tablas analiticas para la clasificacion de los coleopteros de la Peninsula Iberica. Adephaga: I Cicindelidae, II Carabidae. J. Bosch, Barcelona, 415 pp." type="book" year="1927">Fuente (1927)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493588E05F6A0F83FFA9AF803" author="Antoine, M." box="[1181,1355,1965,1992]" pageId="1" pageNumber="485" pagination="315 - 465" refId="ref10238" refString="Antoine, M. (1959) Coleopteres Carabiques du Maroc. Troisieme partie. Memoires de la Societe des Sciences Naturelles et Physiques du Maroc, Nouvelle Serie, Zoologie, 6, 315 - 465." type="journal article" year="1959">Antoine (1959)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493588E05F76BF83CFF35F820" author="Wrase, D. W." pageId="1" pageNumber="485" pagination="889 - 899" refId="ref12584" refString="Wrase, D. W. (2009) On the identity of Amblystomus levantinus Reitter, 1893, and remarks on A. metallescens (Dejean, 1829) (Coleoptera, Carabidae, Harpalini, Amblystomina). Linzer Biologische Beitrage, 41, 889 - 899." type="journal article" year="2009">Wrase (2009)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493588E05F2D2F840FDD9F820" author="Wrase, D. W. &amp; Magrini, P." box="[239,520,2001,2028]" pageId="1" pageNumber="485" pagination="1 - 81" refId="ref12688" refString="Wrase, D. W. &amp; Magrini, P. (2012) Taxonomic revision of the Mediterranean species of genus Amblystomus Erichson, 1837, with description of a new species (Coleoptera, Carabidae, Harpalini, Amblystomina). Annali del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale &quot; G. Doria &quot;, 104, 1 - 81." type="journal article" year="2012">Wrase &amp; Magrini (2012)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493588E05F02EF840FCF1F827" author="Kataev, B. M. &amp; Wrase, D. W." box="[531,800,2001,2028]" pageId="1" pageNumber="485" pagination="251 - 279" refId="ref11539" refString="Kataev, B. M. &amp; Wrase, D. W. (2016) Taxonomic and faunistic notes on certain Anisodactylina, Harpalina, Ditomina and Amblystomina from the Palaearctic, Ethiopian and Oriental regions (Coleoptera: Carabidae: Harpalini). Vernate, 35, 251 - 279." type="journal article" year="2016">Kataev &amp; Wrase (2016)</bibRefCitation>
, etc.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCD36A5935B8E06F2FAFF05FF31FF1E" blockId="2.[151,1436,151,213]" pageId="2" pageNumber="486">
The species is distributed from the Mediterranean Basin to Central Asia (
<collectingCountry id="F3657635935B8E06F60EFF05FB67FF7A" box="[1075,1206,151,177]" name="Uzbekistan" pageId="2" pageNumber="486">Uzbekistan</collectingCountry>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B54935B8E06F6FBFF05FA4DFF7A" author="Wrase, D. W. &amp; Magrini, P." box="[1222,1436,151,177]" pageId="2" pageNumber="486" pagination="1 - 81" refId="ref12688" refString="Wrase, D. W. &amp; Magrini, P. (2012) Taxonomic revision of the Mediterranean species of genus Amblystomus Erichson, 1837, with description of a new species (Coleoptera, Carabidae, Harpalini, Amblystomina). Annali del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale &quot; G. Doria &quot;, 104, 1 - 81." type="journal article" year="2012">Wrase &amp; Magrini,</bibRefCitation>
2012).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
